## 🔐 Security Considerations

- Miner authentication required
- Job result verification prevents false completion claims
- Reward distribution is transparent (blockchain transactions)
- Score manipulation detection (unusual score changes flagged)

## 📈 Performance Targets

- Miner registration: <100ms
- Job assignment: <200ms
- Scoring update: <50ms
- Reward distribution: <1s per miner (blockchain transaction)
- Job queue throughput: >100 jobs/second

